{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384370/extras/RM-993_Tech_Reaper_Loadout.jpg?t=1733538202\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FORGE. DESTROY. EVOLVE.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a walking arsenal in SAND EATERS, a hybrid genre sci-fi shooter set in a dark future plagued by rapidly evolving nanomachine lifeforms called Hive Golems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384370/extras/SE_livingweapon.gif?t=1733538202\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">LIVING WEAPON</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Modify your cybernetic body to grant enhanced combat benefits to firepower, mobility, and durability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384370/extras/SE_playtest.gif?t=1733538202\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FLUID COMBAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a dynamic combat system giving you extreme mobility and opening new ways to express movement and gunplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384370/extras/SE_Environments.gif?t=1733538202\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">IMMERSIVE ENVIRONMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each location in Sand Eaters is handcrafted to deliver rich gameplay and visuals, immersing you in dynamic environments filled with intricate details.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384370/extras/SE_arsenal.gif?t=1733538202\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> DEEP LOADOUT CUSTOMIZATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mech-genre style loadout customization that allows you to forge the perfect arsenal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384370/extras/SE_evolvingenemies.gif?t=1733538202\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EVOLVING ENEMIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Hive Golem lifeforms can re-construct themselves mid-combat capable of evolving into a larger threat. Deal with them swiftly and destroy their cores to reduce them to nothing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384370/extras/SE_playtest2.gif?t=1733538202\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>More coming soon! Wishlist now!</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For regular updates follow Sand Eaters on YouTube and check out the website.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game developed by Fiddler Crab Studios<br><br>for business inquiries and questions fill out the contact form on the Sand Eaters website. <br>Thank you!  <br> </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384370/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733538202","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384370/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733538202","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384370/53930347097542dc5a2cfad046ad07f1a8c8d9d7/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733538202","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384370/53930347097542dc5a2cfad046ad07f1a8c8d9d7/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733538202","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"co